
Makefile.in
    Makefile template
    configure script transforms to create final makefile

configure script 
    generated by autotools
    options customize install
    If no configure autoreconf -i
    
Autotools
Tutorial: https://eklitzke.org/how-to-autotools

./configure generates Makefile
if Makefile already present in source is not autotools

Install prefix 
./configure --prefix=/usr/local

cmake
    alternative build-tool
    generates makefile


make build targets
    install     run as root
    clean       remove old object files
    -n          preview build


    
